as a green mob then their is even a higher chance of success depending on level difference. Furthermore, while the fear is in effect you can not run behind it wacking it without breaking the fear immediately and gaining agro again. And any add on mobs in a fight can work the same way. YOU Intimidate it away. You can further make this skill so that reload time is not as quick as a FD reload.  <HR></BLOCKQUOTE><P>As has already been pointed out, this is flash of light with a memblur effect and possible longer duration (since you never stated how long they would be feared).  But of course there is also the possibility of a shorter duration since you said the duration is random.  So when this skill fails, or the duration wears out too soon you'll end up using flash of light anyway.  Si this really isn't a good contribution to the class.<P>I am all for the posting of good ideas.  Not ideas that are neither helpful, or as you stated, posted to get a rise out of people.
